1
00:01:09,720 --> 00:01:11,920
These three trucks passed Sanjiadian.

2
00:01:12,080 --> 00:01:13,000
From 3:00 p.m.,

3
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:15,520
they disappeared from the cameras for three hours.

4
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:16,920
They reappeared at 6:00.

5
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,760
Is there no footage from that time?

6
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:21,620
It's a small road with no cameras.

7
00:01:22,039 --> 00:01:24,440
Can we find out which company these trucks belong to?

8
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:26,970
These three trucks belong to Tongda Company.

9
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:33,140
You stopped at Sanjiadian for over three hours.

10
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:34,020
What did you do?

11
00:01:34,240 --> 00:01:34,920
We were...

12
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:36,240
we went to eat.

13
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:38,400
Eating for over three hours?

14
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:39,479
Where is your manager?

15
00:01:39,479 --> 00:01:41,340
Manager Chen treated us to a meal.

16
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:43,120
Then we fell asleep.

17
00:01:43,759 --> 00:01:45,360
Was there anything strange?

18
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,640
The driving...

19
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:48,000
the mileage is wrong.

20
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,420
There are many extra kilometers.

21
00:01:50,479 --> 00:01:51,120
When unloading,

22
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:53,039
didn't you notice any problems with the steel bars?

23
00:01:53,039 --> 00:01:55,100
It was dark, we couldn't see clearly.

24
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:55,720
Okay.

25
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:57,600
Thank you, gentlemen.

26
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:59,240
I'll contact you if anything else comes up.

27
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:01,040
Thank you for your cooperation.

28
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:06,600
Thanks.

29
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,610
I'll tell you later.

30
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:13,280
Manager Chen of the Materials Department

31
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:13,940
is missing.

32
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:16,010
Chen Hao really is suspicious.

33
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,120
Ye Qiming is very likely

34
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,450
framed by him this time.

35
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,329
Let's go.

36
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:30,000
Based on the extra distance the trucks traveled,

37
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:30,930
it's right here.

38
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:33,320
Hello.

39
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,700
Please cooperate with us.

40
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:37,480
Hello.

41
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:39,760
Do you have a lot of that steel outside in stock?

42
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:40,400
Not much left.

43
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,520
We have 50 tons left.

44
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:43,380
We just sold 30 tons a few days ago.

45
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:44,600
We heard that

46
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,960
the quality of your steel has some issues.

47
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,090
That's impossible.

48
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:49,840
We only supply for private houses.

49
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:52,240
We don't do business for multi-story buildings.

50
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,900
How much is your steel per ton?

51
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:55,620
Over 2,000.

52
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:57,600
It's cheaper than usual anyway,

53
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:58,560
relatively speaking.

54
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,220
You just said you sold 30 tons.

55
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:01,920
Which company bought it?

56
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,780
And how many trucks did they send?

57
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,660
I have the surveillance footage.

58
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:11,080
It seems to be those cars.

59
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,440
Send these to the Work Safety Bureau.

60
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:15,040
Ye Qiming should be out soon.

61
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:16,200
But isn't Chen Hao

62
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,730
making it a bit too obvious?

63
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,840
Even if we don't intervene,

64
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,600
the Work Safety Bureau will figure it out.

65
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:23,130
He's so blatant and isn't afraid of anything.

66
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:25,240
Someone must be protecting him.

67
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:30,480
Whether it is work safety administration or the police,

68
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:33,120
they can certainly find out if they investigate.

69
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:35,520
Get this kid out of here quickly.

70
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,770
I have already let him run away.

71
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:40,520
Don't let the police find him.

72
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:42,120
Rest assured.

73
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:44,090
If he dares to come back,

74
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,300
I will shut him up for good.

75
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,040
Qiming.

76
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,720
Is there any news from there?

77
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,280
Have you found out the result?

78
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,410
It is already clear.

79
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,680
It was Chen Hao from the building materials department

80
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:10,360
who replaced them with inferior steel bars,

81
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,890
which caused the accident.

82
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:12,800
Chen Hao?

83
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:15,180
What about him? Did you catch him?

84
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,019
He escaped.

85
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:21,519
What happened?

86
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:24,720
Why was Ye Qiming released so quickly?

87
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,320
Those two cops investigating Tian Liang's case

88
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:28,780
have been making trouble.

89
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:31,180
It seems they have too much free time.

90
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:33,240
Let's give them something to do.

91
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,170
What do you mean?

92
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,730
Tian Liang was your man.

93
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:38,159
Don't you suspect Ye Qiming killed him?

94
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:40,280
Give them some clues.

95
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:43,800
We probably won't even need to deal with Ye Qiming ourselves.

96
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,530
Understood.

97
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:51,280
Severely punish the corrupt Ye Qiming! Give back our health!

98
00:04:51,280 --> 00:04:53,640
Punish Ye Qiming! Give back our health!

99
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,200
You go back. I'll take over.

100
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:55,680
Go back.

101
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:58,159
Punish Ye Qiming! Give back our health!

102
00:04:58,360 --> 00:05:00,720
Punish Ye Qiming! Give back our health!

103
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:01,720
Everyone, please.

104
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,520
This is a home.

105
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:04,440
Let's go to the company to talk about it.

106
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:04,960
Okay?

107
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:07,160
My Old Li is still in a coma.

108
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:08,720
Tell me what we should do.

109
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,320
Stop it.

110
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,700
Come with us right now.

111
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:13,160
What are you doing?

112
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:15,000
Let go! Stop it!

113
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,800
Will this solve the problem?

114
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,840
How will you solve it then?

115
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:19,080
Since we promised you,

116
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,560
we will definitely figure something out.

117
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:21,240
Rest assured, everyone.

118
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,400
They are my employees.

119
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:23,520
I will take full responsibility.

120
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:24,680
Please go back first, okay?

121
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,400
Why should we?

122
00:05:25,400 --> 00:05:25,920
Yeah!

123
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:27,500
Solve it right now.

124
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,280
You must solve it for us right now.

125
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:29,680
Let go.

126
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,600
The police are here to help you solve the problem.

127
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,280
How?

128
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,159
The police came just in time.

129
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:38,080
I promise you all in front of the officers

130
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:39,680
that I will definitely give you an answer.

131
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,409
You promise?

132
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,200
What makes you think you can promise that?

133
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:42,200
Ma'am, calm down.

134
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,000
You must trust us.

135
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:46,000
Trust that we will figure out this case.

136
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,640
If he really used inferior rebar

137
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:48,400
resulting in deaths,

138
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:50,440
then they certainly won't escape the law.

139
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:51,680
Stop making a scene, everyone.

140
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,540
Please go back.

141
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:55,220
We will definitely give you an explanation.

142
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,320
The... the police are here.

143
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:56,920
The police are here.

144
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,159
Why don't we go back first?

145
00:05:58,159 --> 00:05:58,840
Please go back.

146
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,970
All right, let's listen to the police.

147
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:01,530
Let's go.

148
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:06,850
Are you okay?

149
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:07,400
I'm fine.

150
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:08,320
Thank you.

151
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:09,880
We heard you were released,

152
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,880
so we dropped by.

153
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:11,280
Yeah.

154
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,400
Speaking of which,

155
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:14,320
I really should thank you two.

156
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,840
If you hadn't found out

157
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:17,040
about the inferior rebar,

158
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,760
I wouldn't have been released so quickly.

159
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:20,360
It's because you're innocent.

160
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,320
If you were really guilty,

161
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,520
no one could help you.

162
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:23,280
Yes.

163
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,480
Even if we can't catch Chen Hao,

164
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,240
the accident happened on my site.

165
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:29,100
I will take full responsibility.

166
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,880
Are you two here

167
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:33,320
for Lu Yang's case?

168
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:35,480
I've been...

169
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,400
well,

170
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,540
you've seen it.

171
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:39,920
Can you give me a few days before we...

172
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,520
Sure.

173
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,320
We'll wait for your call.

174
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:44,040
Thank you for understanding.

175
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:44,640
Thank you.

176
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:45,540
See you two.

177
00:06:46,159 --> 00:06:46,690
Goodbye.

178
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,010
Are you okay?

179
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:51,760
I'm fine.

180
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,360
Let's go back.

181
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,800
Do you think Ye Qiming knows?

182
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,360
Ye Qiming is such a shrewd man.

183
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:12,480
I think he knows whatever tricks his people are pulling.

184
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:15,280
But right now, there's no telling who did it.

185
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,250
Let's go.

186
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:24,440
It's been raining every day lately.

187
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:26,770
It washed away whatever traces were left.

188
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:28,320
Zhao.

189
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:30,600
Captain Shen.

190
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,400
We found bloodstains in a truck.

191
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:32,840
Okay.

192
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,040
Call the trace evidence team.

193
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,440
Got it.

194
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:36,380
Captain Jiang.

195
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,610
A couple of days ago,

196
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:38,480
I heard someone say

197
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,740
they saw Chen Hao on the night of the 25th,

198
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,600
loading sand onto a rebar truck.

199
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,280
Isn't that truck specifically for rebars?

200
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:45,480
Why load it with sand?

201
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,120
Why?

202
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:00,840
Mom.

203
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:02,960
Ye Yuan.

204
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:05,640
Why are you back?

205
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:06,280
When did you come back?

206
00:08:06,280 --> 00:08:07,560
You didn't even tell Mom.

207
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,620
Let Mom look at you.

208
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:09,760
Why have you gotten thinner again?

209
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:10,200
Mom.

210
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,010
How have you been recently?

211
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:12,960
I'm fine.

212
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:14,700
When did you come back?

213
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,480
I came back today. Just got back.

214
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:21,120
Since when did you learn to lie?

215
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:23,520
You don't look like you just got off a plane.

216
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,620
Where is your luggage?

217
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:27,120
I came back yesterday evening.

218
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,320
I left my luggage at the hotel.

219
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,480
Why did you leave it at the hotel?

220
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,880
You have a home to live in.

221
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:32,520
I heard from Yu Na

222
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:35,280
that something happened to our company recently.

223
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:36,809
How did you two get in touch?

224
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,159
She went to my place for a trip.

225
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,320
I think she is pretty

226
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:40,360
and cheerful.

227
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:42,520
Do you know her well?

228
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:44,520
Do you know what kind of person Yu Na is?

229
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:46,250
How far have you two developed?

230
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,600
What are you thinking?

231
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,720
I just like her.

232
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:52,680
But she thinks I'm just a kid.

233
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:53,800
Your current task

234
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,050
is to study hard.

235
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:56,760
You are not allowed to have any contact with Yu Na.

236
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:57,890
Let me take you back.

237
00:08:58,280 --> 00:08:58,960
Mom.

238
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,320
Come with me.

239
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:01,770
Hurry up.

240
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,040
Mom,

241
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:07,680
I want to see Yuna again.

242
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:10,000
Didn't I make myself clear?

243
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,160
I said from now on,

244
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:12,280
you two are not allowed to have any contact.

245
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,340
Do you understand?

246
00:09:14,920 --> 00:09:16,200
What are you doing?

247
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,720
What do you mean, what am I doing?

248
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:19,200
I told you. Do you know her well?

249
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,320
Being with her will ruin you.

250
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,200
You know that?

251
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:22,720
What's wrong with Yuna?

252
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:24,480
As long as it's not her, anyone is fine.

253
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,540
Do you understand?

254
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:29,200
What are you doing, Ye Yuan?

255
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,120
Are you crazy?

256
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:31,560
Mom,

257
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:33,420
stop meddling in my business.

258
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,320
Son.

259
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:37,040
Please, I'm begging you. All right?

260
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:38,280
Listen to me just this once.

261
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:39,960
I'll explain it to you later when I have the chance.

262
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:40,360
All right?

263
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,320
I'm begging you.

264
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:50,500
I won't be stubborn with you anymore.

265
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:00,770
You're back.

266
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:04,760
What's wrong?

267
00:10:04,760 --> 00:10:05,560
Are you upset?

268
00:10:06,160 --> 00:10:07,820
Your son is back. Did you know?

269
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:08,360
Really?

270
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,500
Where is he?

271
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:10,740
I sent him away.

272
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:12,560
Why?

273
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,480
Yu Na went to find Ye Yuan.

274
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:15,840
I don't know how

275
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,370
the two of them got in touch.

276
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,440
Isn't this nonsense?

277
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:22,480
And Ye Yuan also

278
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:24,210
came back especially for Yu Na.

279
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:31,120
Can you stay away from that Yu Na?

280
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,200
Look at what she has done

281
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,400
to our family.

282
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:36,440
It's because of the company's business needs.

283
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,520
I don't care.

284
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,940
My child is my bottom line.

285
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:42,850
I can't let her hurt him no matter what.

286
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:44,980
You go and handle this.

287
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:47,120
Go.

288
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,920
Okay, I'll go.

289
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,060
Comrade Jiang Tao,

290
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:24,850
what is this?

291
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:29,040
Ye Qiming is your classmate.

292
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,360
The letter reports

293
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:32,120
that during the land bidding process,

294
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,180
you manipulated it

295
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:34,800
and accepted bribes.

296
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:38,720
Is there any evidence?

297
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:41,480
Room 202, Building 16, Yuhuayuan Neighborhood.

298
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:42,660
What's that about?

299
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:44,580
It's like this.

300
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,570
I wasn't in office at that time.

301
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:48,000
My parents lived in the countryside,

302
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,440
and they were in poor health.

303
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:52,370
I wanted to bring them to the city to take care of them.

304
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:54,810
But I didn't have money to buy a house then.

305
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,720
So Ye Qiming

306
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,800
let my parents live in one of his apartments.

307
00:11:57,800 --> 00:12:01,000
We agreed that I would pay him back in installments later.

308
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,120
Comrade Jiang Tao,

309
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:02,880
we are here this time

310
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,740
just to investigate this matter.

311
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:07,080
I hope you can cooperate with our investigation.

312
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:07,740
No problem.

313
00:12:08,160 --> 00:12:10,720
I am willing to accept the organization's investigation.

314
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:12,580
How is your investigation going?

315
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:14,280
I have found out, Mr. Ye.

316
00:12:14,280 --> 00:12:16,000
This 10 million was taken by

317
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:18,180
the financial director, Manager Yu.

318
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:19,920
Where did she transfer the money?

319
00:12:19,920 --> 00:12:21,920
To an overseas catering company.

320
00:12:22,040 --> 00:12:24,100
The legal representative is Ye Yuan.

321
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:31,520
From now on,

322
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,280
without my approval,

323
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:35,400
not a single cent from the company's account can be moved.

324
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:36,400
Do you understand?

325
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,130
Understood.

326
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:38,410
Alright.

327
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,980
You can go back to work.

328
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:49,600
Ye Yuan is still involved.

329
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:00,400
Hello.

330
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:02,460
The city had a talk with Jiang Tao.

331
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:05,730
We need to add some fuel to the fire.

332
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:08,360
Okay.

333
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:10,130
Adding fuel to the fire.

334
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:21,440
How is it, Lao Jin?

335
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:22,800
The report is out.

336
00:13:22,800 --> 00:13:23,320
The DNA on the shovel

337
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:24,520
and in the truck

338
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:26,220
all belongs to Tian Liang.

339
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:31,960
Great.

340
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:33,400
This confirms

341
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,880
that this is the secondary crime scene.

342
00:13:35,880 --> 00:13:38,960
Using the sand and the fleet to dispose of the body at the sand quarry.

343
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:39,600
Smart.

344
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:41,900
No wonder we couldn't find anything.

345
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:42,920
Thanks, Lao Jin.

346
00:13:42,920 --> 00:13:43,850
Get back to work.

347
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:47,400
According to the team's account,

348
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:48,600
we can basically confirm

349
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,200
that Chen Hao is the suspect.

350
00:13:51,040 --> 00:13:51,800
Since yesterday,

351
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:53,160
Chen Hao has been missing.

352
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:54,520
The wanted poster has been issued.

353
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:56,080
He can't escape Tongjiang City.

354
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:56,480
So,

355
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:57,800
let's split into two groups.

356
00:13:57,800 --> 00:13:58,200
Zhao,

357
00:13:58,480 --> 00:13:59,340
you lead a group

358
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,960
and stake out his previous residence.

359
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:01,400
Li,

360
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:03,360
I'll leave the rest to you.

361
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:05,360
Stake out all the abandoned factories in the city.

362
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,600
He definitely wouldn't dare to stay in a hotel.

363
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:08,080
Report any news immediately.

364
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:08,520
Action.

365
00:14:08,520 --> 00:14:08,960
Okay.

366
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:10,250
Let's go.

367
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:14,800
After investigating for so long,

368
00:14:14,800 --> 00:14:16,460
it's finally coming to an end.

369
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:26,080
What's wrong? Why the long face?

370
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:30,520
I don't know.

371
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,200
I see.

372
00:14:32,520 --> 00:14:34,920
You are clean. What can they report you for?

373
00:14:37,680 --> 00:14:38,960
Illegally giving you land,

374
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:40,240
leaking the bid,

375
00:14:40,680 --> 00:14:41,740
accepting bribes,

376
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:44,200
Room 202, Building 16, Yuhuayuan Neighborhood,

377
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,860
using personal connections.

378
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:47,570
That's about it.

379
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:49,800
I know who did it.

380
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:56,400
Qiming.

381
00:14:57,640 --> 00:14:59,040
Regarding my promotion,

382
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:01,560
what exactly did you do?
